      <div class="proc-d" data-en="Weekly bid adjustments, A/B testing of headlines, keyword expansion and Optiscore improvements to keep results moving upward." data-es="Ajustes de puja semanales, pruebas A/B de titulares, expansión de palabras clave y mejoras de Optiscore." data-sq="Rregullime javore të ofertave, teste A/B të headlines, zgjerim fjalëkyçesh dhe përmirësime Optiscore." data-da="Ugentlige budjusteringer, A/B-testning af overskrifter, søgeordsudvidelse og Optiscore-forbedringer.">Weekly bid adjustments, A/B testing of headlines, keyword expansion and Optiscore improvements to keep results moving upward.</div>
