      <h4 data-en="Barcelona Based, Globally Serving" data-es="Basados en Barcelona, Clientes Globales" data-sq="Bazuar në Barcelona, Shërbejmë Globalisht" data-da="Barcelona-baseret, Globalt Servicerende">Barcelona Based, Globally Serving</h4>
      <p data-en="We are based in Barcelona and work with clients worldwide. Distance is never a barrier — we run campaigns across Europe and beyond from our base in Spain." data-es="Estamos en Barcelona y trabajamos con clientes en todo el mundo. La distancia nunca es una barrera — gestionamos campañas en toda Europa y más allá." data-sq="Jemi bazuar në Barcelona dhe punojmë me klientë në mbarë botën. Distanca nuk është kurrë pengesë." data-da="Vi er baseret i Barcelona og arbejder med kunder verden over. Afstand er aldrig en barriere — vi kører kampagner i hele Europa og videre.">We are based in Barcelona and work with clients worldwide. Distance is never a barrier — we run campaigns across Europe and beyond from our base in Spain.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card reveal">
      <div class="why-num">02</div>
      <h4 data-en="5 Languages, Zero Barriers" data-es="5 Idiomas, Cero Barreras" data-sq="5 Gjuhë, Zero Barriera" data-da="5 Sprog, Nul Barrierer">5 Languages, Zero Barriers</h4>
      <p data-en="We work fluently in Danish, Albanian, English, Spanish and Italian. You communicate in your language — no middlemen, no lost nuance, no translation issues." data-es="Trabajamos con fluidez en danés, albanés, inglés, español e italiano. Comunícate en tu idioma — sin intermediarios ni problemas de traducción." data-sq="Punojmë rrjedhshëm në danisht, shqip, anglisht, spanjisht dhe italisht. Komunikoni në gjuhën tuaj — pa ndërmjetës." data-da="Vi arbejder flydende på dansk, albansk, engelsk, spansk og italiensk. Kommuniker på dit eget sprog — ingen mellemmænd, ingen tabte nuancer.">We work fluently in Danish, Albanian, English, Spanish and Italian. You communicate in your language — no middlemen, no lost nuance, no translation issues.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card reveal">
      <div class="why-num">03</div>
      <h4 data-en="Google Ads Specialists" data-es="Especialistas en Google Ads" data-sq="Specialistë të Google Ads" data-da="Google Ads Specialister">Google Ads Specialists</h4>
      <p data-en="We are not a generalist agency. Google Ads is our core focus — Conversion Tracking, PMAX, AI Max, Smart Bidding — we know every tool and use it to grow your results." data-es="No somos una agencia generalista. Google Ads es nuestro foco principal — conocemos cada herramienta y la usamos para hacer crecer tus resultados." data-sq="Nuk jemi një agenci generaliste. Google Ads është fokusi ynë kryesor — njohim çdo mjet dhe e përdorim për të rritur rezultatet tuaja." data-da="Vi er ikke et generalistbureau. Google Ads er vores kerneområde — vi kender hvert eneste værktøj og bruger det til at vokse dine resultater.">We are not a generalist agency. Google Ads is our core focus — Conversion Tracking, PMAX, AI Max, Smart Bidding — we know every tool and use it to grow your results.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card reveal">
      <div class="why-num">04</div>
      <h4 data-en="No Long Contracts" data-es="Sin Contratos Largos" data-sq="Pa Kontrata Afatgjata" data-da="Ingen Lange Kontrakter">No Long Contracts</h4>
      <p data-en="Monthly rolling service with 30 days notice. We earn your business every month through results — not by locking you in. Transparency and performance are our contract." data-es="Servicio mensual con 30 días de preaviso. Nos ganamos tu negocio cada mes con resultados — no con bloqueos. La transparencia y el rendimiento son nuestro contrato." data-sq="Shërbim mujor me 30 ditë njoftim. Ne fitojmë biznesin tuaj çdo muaj me rezultate — jo duke ju bllokuar." data-da="Månedlig løbende service med 30 dages varsel. Vi fortjener din forretning hver måned gennem resultater — ikke ved at låse dig fast.">Monthly rolling service with 30 days notice. We earn your business every month through results — not by locking you in. Transparency and performance are our contract.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
