    <h2 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:42px;letter-spacing:-2px;line-height:1.06;color:#fff;margin-bottom:12px;" id="tools-h2">Four tools. Completely free. Powered by AI.</h2>
