      <h3 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.8px;color:#12111e;margin-bottom:8px;" id="audit-title">60-Second Website Audit</h3>
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:#5c5b72;margin-bottom:28px;line-height:1.65;" id="audit-desc">Tell us your website and your biggest frustration. Our AI gives you three concrete, actionable recommendations personalised to your business.</p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:16px;">
